Business Talk with Michael Avery is South Africa’s leading online business talk show, making it the perfect place for your company to position itself as a market leader. Business Talk has excellent marketing solutions which allow your company to feature on the show. These include: Executive Interview Package
Season Sponsorship Business Talk sponsors to date have included Discovery Bank, EY, Discovery Business Insurance, EY-Parthenon, Sage, Microsoft, and Monocle. Guests on the show have included the biggest names in business: Andrew Golding, chief executive of the Pam Golding Property group; Sim Tshabalala, joint chief executive of the Standard Bank Group; Michael Jordaan, Bank Zero Cofounder; Lillian Barnard, Microsoft South Africa CEO; Magda Wierzycka, co-founder of Sygnia, and Jacques Celliers, First National Bank CEO. Highly-respected radio and TV personality Michael Avery then hosts the show. Avery is well known in business circles for his roles on Classic FM and Business Day TV – and as the anchor of the HOT Business show on HOT 1027. As part of the BusinessTech stable, we make it easy for your company to take part in Business Talk. A Business Talk interview package sees an executive of your choice appearing on the show, with the interview published on the Business Talk website, BusinessTech, YouTube, Facebook, and Spotify – reaching an engaged audience. For sustained exposure, a Business Talk sponsorship provides the participating company with exclusive brand placements across both the Business Talk and BusinessTech platforms for a full season of the show. To find out more about Business Talk, contact BusinessTech’s marketing team.